        <a href="/downloads/medication-list.csv">📊 <strong>Medication List (Spreadsheet CSV)</strong></a><br />
        <small>Can be opened in Google Sheets, Excel, or any spreadsheet program.</small>
        </li>

        <li>
        <a href="https://honorable-mimosa-4f3.notion.site/Medication-Supplement-Tracker-2483e9ff50d88092acecd7dad5902746?source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">📘 <strong>Notion Medication & Supplement Tracker</strong></a><br />
